ivardefs.name: capability_
ivardefs.desc: Device capabilities.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details for an organization or a particular human that is responsible for the device.

ivardefs.name: deviceName_
ivardefs.desc: A name given to the device to identify it.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Unique instance identifiers assigned to a device by the software, manufacturers, other organizations or owners. For example: handle ID.

ivardefs.name: languageCode_
ivardefs.desc: Language code for the human-readable text strings produced by the device (all supported).

ivardefs.name: material_
ivardefs.desc: A substance used to create the material(s) of which the device is made.

ivardefs.name: modelNumber
ivardefs.desc: The model number for the device.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Descriptive information, usage information or implantation information that is not captured in an existing element.

ivardefs.name: onlineInformation
ivardefs.desc: Access to on-line information about the device.

ivardefs.name: owner
ivardefs.desc: An organization that is responsible for the provision and ongoing maintenance of the device.

ivardefs.name: parentDevice
ivardefs.desc: The parent device it can be part of.

ivardefs.name: physicalCharacteristics
ivardefs.desc: Dimensions, color etc.

ivardefs.name: property_
ivardefs.desc: The actual configuration settings of a device as it actually operates, e.g., regulation status, time properties.

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: The quantity of the device present in the packaging (e.g. the number of devices present in a pack, or the number of devices in the same package of the medicinal product).

ivardefs.name: safety_
ivardefs.desc: Safety characteristics of the device.

ivardefs.name: shelfLifeStorage_
ivardefs.desc: Shelf Life and storage information.

ivardefs.name: specialization_
ivardefs.desc: The capabilities supported on a  device, the standards to which the device conforms for a particular purpose, and used for the communication.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: What kind of device or device system this is.

ivardefs.name: udiDeviceIdentifier_
ivardefs.desc: Unique device identifier (UDI) assigned to device label or package.  Note that the Device may include multiple udiCarriers as it either may include just the udiCarrier for the jurisdiction it is sold, or for multiple jurisdictions it could have been sold.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: A network address on which the device may be contacted directly.

ivardefs.name: version_
ivardefs.desc: The available versions of the device, e.g., software versions.

properties.desc: The characteristics, operational status and capabilities of a medical-related component of a medical device.
